        How Buyers' Borrowing Capacity Affects Brisbane Property Sellers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        When interest rates move, what buyers can borrow changes, and that directly affects what they can pay. Here is how sellers can factor borrowing capacity into their pricing and campaign approach.
      </p>
